headline: Farmina Pet Foods Expands U.S. Veterinary Presence with National Distribution Agreement with MWI Animal Health
summary: Farmina Pet Foods, a global leader in premium pet nutrition, has signed a national distribution agreement with MWI Animal Health (MWI), a leading provider of veterinary solutions and a part of Cencora (formerly AmerisourceBergen). Through this partnership, MWI will market and distribute Farmina's VetLife line of therapeutic diets, increasing access to science-backed, natural pet nutrition for veterinary practices and pet families across the United States.
